resources.string:
If remote provision enabled, provision process will be:

 1. Scan for an unprovisioned device, connect and provision;

 2. Keep the connection state, send scan command to the device;

 3. Some remote devices info will be upload;

 4. Check and do provision one by one;

If fast provision enabled, provision process will be:

 1. Scan for an unprovisioned device, connect;

 2. With the connection, get all unprovisioned devices; Device info with mac address will be in response message;

 3. Set device address by mac address one by one;

 4. Set provisioning data;
